  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to assess the effect of participating in the interactive
      hypertension education program of the German Hypertension League (DHL©) &quot;My blood pressure -
      OK!&quot; on office systolic blood pressure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
